        <section id="what-is" class="card" style="margin-bottom:12px">
          <h2>What is Peak 301?</h2>
          <p><strong>Peak 301</strong> is a soy-based roof rejuvenation treatment engineered to extend the life of asphalt shingles by stopping granular loss, restoring flexibility, and improving water resistance. It's applied quickly and safely by trained contractors — without replacing the roof.</p>
          <ul class="benefits">
            <li><strong>Extend roof life</strong> — adds years of service life when applied correctly.</li>
            <li><strong>Stops granule loss</strong> — reduces weathering and premature failure.</li>
            <li><strong>Restores flexibility</strong> — rejuvenates asphalt for better performance in heat and cold.</li>
            <li><strong>Fast install</strong> — quick, serviceable jobs that add recurring revenue.</li>
          </ul>

          <p style="margin-top:8px;font-weight:700">Peak 301 vs roof replacement: lower cost, faster installation, minimal disruption — ideal for homeowners not yet ready for replacement.</p>

          <p style="margin-top:12px;font-size:14px">Download the technical spec: <a href="assets/peak301-spec.pdf" target="_blank">Peak 301 Technical PDF</a> · <a href="assets/peak301-sds.pdf" target="_blank">Safety Data Sheet (SDS)</a></p>
        </section>

